हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Kiara, a self-made billionaire heiress, gives up her identity for love — only to be discarded by Aryan, a proud businessman who believes she married him for money. Heartbroken and humiliated, she vanishes. But when she returns, it’s not as his wife — it’s as a force he never saw coming. As secrets unravel and egos clash, love, betrayal, and revenge ignite a storm where only one can win.
